#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.179"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.179:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.179:0.2"
msgid "18. Sañcetaniyavagga"
msgstr "18. Intention"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: parinibbānahetusuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.179:0.3"
msgid "179. Nibbānasutta"
msgstr "179. Extinguishment"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.179:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yenāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"āyasmatā sāriputtena saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda went up to Venerable Sāriputta, and exchanged "
"greetings with him."

msgctxt "an4.179:1.2"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho āyasmā ānando āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, Ānanda sat down to one "
"side, and said to Sāriputta:"

msgctxt "an4.179:1.3"
msgid ""
"“ko nu kho, āvuso sāriputta, hetu ko paccayo, yena m’idhekacce sattā "
"diṭṭheva dhamme na parinibbāyantī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“What is the cause, Reverend Sāriputta, what is the reason why some sentient "
"beings aren’t fully extinguished in the present life?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.179:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāvuso ānanda, sattā imā hānabhāgiyā saññāti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānanti, "
"imā ṭhitibhāgiyā saññāti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānanti, imā visesabhāgiyā saññāti "
"yathābhūtaṃ nappajānanti, imā nibbedhabhāgiyā saññāti yathābhūtaṃ "
"nappajānanti."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Ānanda, it’s because some sentient beings don’t really understand "
"which perceptions make things worse, which keep things steady, which lead to "
"distinction, and which lead to penetration."

msgctxt "an4.179:2.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, āvuso ānanda, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva "
"dhamme na parinibbāyantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s the cause, that’s the reason why some sentient beings aren’t fully "
"extinguished in the present life.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.179:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Ko panāvuso sāriputta, hetu ko paccayo, yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva "
"dhamme parinibbāyantī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“What is the cause, Reverend Sāriputta, what is the reason why some sentient "
"beings are fully extinguished in the present life?”"

msgctxt "an4.179:3.2"
msgid ""
"“Idhāvuso ānanda, sattā imā hānabhāgiyā saññāti yathābhūtaṃ pajānanti, imā "
"ṭhitibhāgiyā saññāti yathābhūtaṃ pajānanti, imā visesabhāgiyā saññāti "
"yathābhūtaṃ pajānanti, imā nibbedhabhāgiyā saññāti yathābhūtaṃ pajānanti."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Ānanda, it’s because some sentient beings truly understand which "
"perceptions make things worse, which keep things steady, which lead to "
"distinction, and which lead to penetration."

msgctxt "an4.179:3.3"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, āvuso ānanda, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva "
"dhamme parinibbāyantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s the cause, that’s the reason why some sentient beings are fully "
"extinguished in the present life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.179:3.4"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
